---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { SITE_CONFIG } from '../../config.js';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import trimImg from '../../assets/gallery/fl/florida-tree-service-2.jpg';
---

<MainLayout 
  title="Professional Tree Trimming & Pruning Florida | Health & Beauty" 
  description="Enhance your curb appeal and tree health with expert trimming. Specialized palm pruning, oak thinning, and structural pruning across Florida."
>
  <header style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1b4332 0%, #081c15 100%); color: white; padding: 6rem 1rem; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem); margin: 0; font-weight: 900;">Trimming & Pruning</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #95d5b2; margin-top: 1rem;">Sculpting Floridaâ€™s landscapes for health, safety, and sunlight.</p>
  </header>

  <main class="container" style="max-width: 900px; padding-top: 4rem; padding-bottom: 12rem;">
    <Image src={trimImg} alt="Professional tree trimming service" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 24px; margin-bottom: 4rem;" />

    <div style="line-height: 1.9; color: #374151; font-size: 1.15rem;">
        <h2 style="color: #064e3b; font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800;">Art Meets Science in Arboriculture</h2>
        <p>In the Florida sun, trees grow with incredible speed. Without regular maintenance, canopies become "top-heavy" and vulnerable to wind. Proper trimming isn't just about cutting branches; it's about <strong>structural integrity</strong> and aesthetic balance.</p>

        <h3 style="color: #064e3b; margin-top: 3rem;">Our Trimming Services:</h3>
        <ul style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            <li><strong>Crown Thinning:</strong> Improving airflow to help trees survive high hurricane winds.</li>
            <li><strong>Specialized Palm Care:</strong> Proper removal of dead fronds and seed pods without damaging the "boot."</li>
            <li><strong>Vista Pruning:</strong> Opening up views of lakes or coastlines without compromising tree health.</li>
            <li><strong>Clearance Pruning:</strong> Keeping limbs safely away from roofs, gutters, and power lines.</li>
        </ul>

        <div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 4rem 0;">
            <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #064e3b;">Boost Your Curb Appeal</h4>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Clean, well-maintained trees can increase your property value by up to 15%. Our network provides seasonal maintenance programs tailored to Florida's unique species like Live Oaks, Royal Palms, and Magnolias.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href={SITE_CONFIG.phoneHref} style="background: #ea580c; color: white !important; padding: 1.5rem 3rem; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 16px; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.5rem; display: inline-block;">
            SCHEDULE YOUR TRIMMING TODAY
        </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</MainLayout>